 result←object tooltip arg
⍝ Allow reading and writing a text vector to be used by onToolTip
⍝ (This is supposed to be just a character vector, but apparently APL+Win allows arbitrary data, so we will too.)
⍝? onToolTip is not presently working in Dyalog
⍝? Toolbox objects use this a different way
⍝? Watch out for classes that need to suppress this

 :If 0=≢arg
     result←object ⎕VGET⊂'_tooltip' ''
 :Else
     object._tooltip←##.Single arg
     result←NoRes
 :EndIf
